Sentencas: In this study, a high-temperature tubular solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) was modeled and optimized from thermodynamical and electrical point of view.
Titulo: Multi-objective optimization of tubular solid oxide fuel cells fed by natural gas: an energetic and exergetic simultaneous optimization

Sentencas: The optimization was carried out by the fast and elitist multi-objective genetic algorithm approach: NSGA-II (non-dominated sorting genetic algorithm II).
Titulo: Multi-objective optimization of tubular solid oxide fuel cells fed by natural gas: an energetic and exergetic simultaneous optimization

Sentencas: The modeled fuel cell was designed with an internal reforming stage.
Titulo: Multi-objective optimization of tubular solid oxide fuel cells fed by natural gas: an energetic and exergetic simultaneous optimization

Sentencas: The natural gas was selected as the inlet fuel which was converted to the hydrogen gas in the internal reformer.
Titulo: Multi-objective optimization of tubular solid oxide fuel cells fed by natural gas: an energetic and exergetic simultaneous optimization

Sentencas: The electrical power of the fuel cell and its exergy destruction were selected as objective functions.
Titulo: Multi-objective optimization of tubular solid oxide fuel cells fed by natural gas: an energetic and exergetic simultaneous optimization

Sentencas: First, the effects of six major parameters of operating temperature, current density, operating pressure, fuel flow rate, airflow rate and air-to-fuel ratio on electrical power and fuel cell exergy destruction were investigated.
Titulo: Multi-objective optimization of tubular solid oxide fuel cells fed by natural gas: an energetic and exergetic simultaneous optimization

Sentencas: The results showed that increasing the operating temperature, operating pressure, air-to-fuel ratio, and airflow rate increased the electrical power and reduced the exergy destruction.
Titulo: Multi-objective optimization of tubular solid oxide fuel cells fed by natural gas: an energetic and exergetic simultaneous optimization

Sentencas: Also, four parameters of operating temperature, current density, operating pressure, and air-to-fuel ratio were selected as independent variables.
Titulo: Multi-objective optimization of tubular solid oxide fuel cells fed by natural gas: an energetic and exergetic simultaneous optimization

Sentencas: The optimization results based on TOPSIS and LINMAP decision-making methods showed that the optimal values of electrical power and fuel cell exergy destruction were 405.1 kW and 22.9 kW, respectively.
Titulo: Multi-objective optimization of tubular solid oxide fuel cells fed by natural gas: an energetic and exergetic simultaneous optimization

Sentencas: According to the Fuzzy decision-making method, the optimal values of power and exergy destruction were 465.2 kW and 95.7 kW, respectively.
Titulo: Multi-objective optimization of tubular solid oxide fuel cells fed by natural gas: an energetic and exergetic simultaneous optimization
